    <title>Linux operation</title>
    <url>/15/Linux%20operation/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Linux"><a href="#Linux" class="headerlink" title="Linux"></a>Linux</h1><h2 id="Linux-commands-commonly"><a href="#Linux-commands-commonly" class="headerlink" title="Linux commands commonly"></a>Linux commands commonly</h2><ul>
<li>ls / ls -a </li>
<li>ll </li>
<li>pwd </li>
<li>cd / </li>
<li>cd or cd ~ </li>
<li>mkdir / mkdir -p   </li>
<li>touch  </li>
<li>cat </li>
<li>rm -f  </li>
<li>rm -rf </li>
<li>vim</li>
<li>vi </li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight txt"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim &amp; vi 二者区别：</span><br><span class="line">1.vim 具有程序编辑的能力，可以以字体颜色辨别语法的正确性，方便程序设计；</span><br><span class="line">2.vim可以当作vi的升级版本，他可以用多种颜色的方式来显示一些特殊的信息</span><br><span class="line">3.vim里面加入了很多额外的功能，例如支持正则表达式的搜索、多文件编辑、块复制等等</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Package-manager-yum"><a href="#Package-manager-yum" class="headerlink" title="Package manager - yum"></a>Package manager - yum</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装</span></span><br><span class="line">yum install -y package(eg.ngnix)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 移除单个或者多个</span></span><br><span class="line">yum remove wget unzip -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Network-or-port-status"><a href="#Network-or-port-status" class="headerlink" title="Network or port status"></a>Network or port status</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看tcp端口是否被占用</span></span><br><span class="line">netstat -nultp</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 过滤选择查看某个端口</span></span><br><span class="line">netstat -anp | grep 8000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Process-status"><a href="#Process-status" class="headerlink" title="Process status"></a>Process status</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看所有进程</span></span><br><span class="line">ps -ef 或者 ps uat -- 区别在于展示风格不同</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 过滤查看mysql进程</span></span><br><span class="line">ps -ef | grep process(eg.mysql)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 查看某个进程的pid</span></span><br><span class="line">pgrep process(eg.mysql)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 杀掉某个进程</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">kill</span> -s 9 pid(eg.12485)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Iptables"><a href="#Iptables" class="headerlink" title="Iptables"></a>Iptables</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 让在安全组配置中的端口可以访问</span></span><br><span class="line">iptables -I INPUT -p tcp -m state --state NEW -m tcp --dport 8087 -j ACCEPT</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Decompression-and-compression"><a href="#Decompression-and-compression" class="headerlink" title="Decompression and compression"></a>Decompression and compression</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 1. zip </span></span><br><span class="line">zip -r demo.zip demo</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 解压xxx.zip 到当前目录</span></span><br><span class="line">unzip xxx.zip -d . </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 2. tar</span></span><br><span class="line">tar zcvf demo.tar.gz demo</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 解压</span></span><br><span class="line">tar -xvf demo.tar</span><br><span class="line">tar -xvf demo.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Connection"><a href="#Connection" class="headerlink" title="Connection"></a>Connection</h2><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># mac terminal or xshell tools like </span></span><br><span class="line">ssh root@119.23.208.xx </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="Upload-or-download-file"><a href="#Upload-or-download-file" class="headerlink" title="Upload or download file"></a>Upload or download file</h2><h3 id="windows"><a href="#windows" class="headerlink" title="windows"></a>windows</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 1. install lrzsz</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 安装</span></span><br><span class="line">yum install lrzsz -y</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 验证</span></span><br><span class="line">rpm -qa | grep lrzsz</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 2. upload</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 弹窗选择文件框</span></span><br><span class="line">rz</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 3. download</span></span><br><span class="line">sz xxx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="mac"><a href="#mac" class="headerlink" title="mac"></a>mac</h3><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 1. upload</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 基于本地终端操作 默认上传到目录为用户目录 如下：我用户目录存在test文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 上传文件</span></span><br><span class="line">scp  docker.md root@119.23.208.253:./test/docker.md</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 上传文件夹 xxx为某个文件夹</span></span><br><span class="line">scp -r xxx root@119.23.208.253:./</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 2. download</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 基于本地终端</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 下载文件</span></span><br><span class="line">scp root@119.23.208.253:/root/docker.md .</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 下载文件夹test</span></span><br><span class="line">scp -r root@119.23.208.253:/root/test .</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


